{"tid":829701,"cid":9,"subCid":0,"title":"屌佢老母有無人今日登入唔到Facebook","createTime":"2018-09-20T15:57:05.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-21T07:00:02.000Z","uid":45029,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"9291ea30f91afdc0656223e8882fd47c0162c147","tid":829701,"uid":45029,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-20T15:57:05.000Z","msg":"今日突然登入唔到facebook<br />\n個acc唔係比人停用，登入無出停用提示，其他人搵到我<br />\n試過哂忘記密碼，用人部機都登入都唔得<br />\n忘記密碼用自己個email同電話都搵唔到個acc<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/09/20/234428_519ccdc671b3c06ff95e875744abd500.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F09%2F20%2F234428_519ccdc671b3c06ff95e875744abd500.png&h=43f0b03b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n用電腦版想忘記自己帳號，出左句<br />\nSorry, something went wrong<br />\nWe are working on getting this fixed as soon as we can<br />\n<br />\n屌佢老母，依家用facebook登入d app全部入唔到<br />\n有無人知咩事，或者一樣情況<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"72c6b94b4380a7b82d12d32c6674d53f57f12485","tid":829701,"uid":26429,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-20T15:59:53.000Z","msg":"我ON到Facbeook啊 無問題 幫樓主你推下啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"01676220e752c0fbc2c4b7d0fc1f8005d4868d4c","tid":829701,"uid":45029,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"72c6b94b4380a7b82d12d32c6674d53f57f12485","tid":829701,"uid":26429,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-20T15:59:53.000Z","msg":"我ON到Facbeook啊 無問題 幫樓主你推下啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-20T16:03:53.000Z","msg":"多謝你<br />\n唉，無左facebook事小，入唔返d app事大"},{"pid":"f004cc5138dfcc4eb58bca26697963009075c5e9","tid":829701,"uid":26429,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-20T16:39:08.000Z","msg":"再幫樓主推一推，好明白玩左好耐既app